                    "script": "\timport traceback\n\t\t\n\tidentifier \u003d self.view.params.profile.nodesetId\n\tnodesetTitle \u003d self.view.params.profile.nodesetTitle\n\t\n\tself.getSibling(\"Progress\").position.display \u003d True\n\t\n\ttry:\n\t\txml \u003d CESMII.UALibraryRESTService.downloadXML(self.session, identifier)\n\t\t(success, error, name, tags) \u003d CESMII.Converter.convert_UANodeSet_to_Ignition(xml, self.session)\n\t\tif success:\n\t\t\tCESMII.Converter.importPopup(name, tags)\n\t\telse:\n\t\t\tCESMII.Converter.showErrorMessage(\"Import Error\", error)\n\texcept:\n\t\tCESMII.Converter.showErrorMessage(\"Import Error\", \"Error importing profile: %s\" % traceback.format_exc())\n\t\t\n\tself.getSibling(\"Progress\").position.display \u003d False"
